OL,3,COriginal Coronation Street cast member
OL,4,CAlan Rothwell dies aged 89
OL,6,FAlan Rothwell, best known for playing
OL,7,FDavid Barlow in the original cast of
OL,8,FITV soap Coronation Street, has died
OL,9,Faged 89, his family have confirmed.
OL,11,FThe Oldham-born actor starred on the
OL,12,Fsoap as the brother of Ken Barlow,
OL,13,Fplayed by William Roache, when it
OL,14,Ffirst launched in 1960 until 1969.
OL,16,FHe died "peacefully in hospital
OL,17,Ffollowing a short illness" on Thursday.
OL,19,FA family statement said the actor will
OL,20,Fbe "fondly remembered and deeply
OL,21,Fmissed".
OL,26,@xD@IOUyD@ZO]|D@DOU}D@GO]
