OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778864757
OL,3,COriginal Coronation Street cast member
OL,4,CAlan Rothwell dies aged 89
OL,6,FThe statement read: "Alan was a
OL,7,Fprofessional radio, television, film
OL,8,Fand stage actor and director whose
OL,9,Fcareer spanned more than 70 years.
OL,11,F"Alan died peacefully in hospital
OL,12,Ffollowing a short illness.
OL,14,F"Beyond his professional achievements,
OL,15,Fhe was a loving husband, father,
OL,16,Fgrandfather and uncle.
OL,18,F"He will be fondly remembered and
OL,19,Fdeeply missed by his family, friends,
OL,20,Fcolleagues and the many people whose
OL,21,Flives he touched through his work."
OL,26,@nD@UOUsD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU}D@cO]
