PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778864757
OL,3,COriginal Coronation Street cast member
OL,4,CAlan Rothwell dies aged 89
OL,6,FBorn in Oldham in 1937, Rothwell was a
OL,7,Fprolific actor in the 1960s, appearing
OL,8,Fin TV series such as Gideon's Way and
OL,9,FThe Villains.
OL,11,FHis role on Coronation Street was
OL,12,Fwritten with him in mind as the
OL,13,Fcreator Tony Warren had worked with
OL,14,Fhim during their childhoods on BBC
OL,15,FRadio's Children's Hour.
OL,17,FRoache paid tribute to the actor,
OL,18,Fsaying: "I am very sorry to hear of
OL,19,FAlan's passing.
OL,26,@zD@IOU
