PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778864757
OL,3,COriginal Coronation Street cast member
OL,4,CAlan Rothwell dies aged 89
OL,6,F"He and I worked together on the very
OL,7,Ffirst episodes of Coronation Street,
OL,8,Fwhich was such a wonderful time, I got
OL,9,Fto know him well over the years, he
OL,10,Fwas a very good actor and a delightful
OL,11,Fman.
OL,13,F"I send my thoughts and condolences to
OL,14,Fhis family."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@LO]
