PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778864757
OL,3,COriginal Coronation Street cast member
OL,4,CAlan Rothwell dies aged 89
OL,6,FRothwell also starred in the Channel 4
OL,7,Fsoap Brookside as Nicholas Black in
OL,8,Fthe 1980s and became a familiar face
OL,9,Fto generations of viewers as the
OL,10,Fpresenter of the long-running
OL,11,Fchildren's television programmes
OL,12,FPicture Box and Hickory House.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for Coronation Street
OL,15,Fsaid: "We're very sorry to hear of
OL,16,FAlan Rothwell's passing and extend our
OL,17,Fsincerest condolences to his family at
OL,18,Fthis very sad time.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
