PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778864757
OL,3,COriginal Coronation Street cast member
OL,4,CAlan Rothwell dies aged 89
OL,6,F"He created an iconic and memorable
OL,7,Fcharacter in David Barlow and will
OL,8,Fforever be remembered as one of the
OL,9,Foriginal cast members of Coronation
OL,10,FStreet."
OL,12,FIn more recent years Rothwell was seen
OL,13,Fin 2013's Alan Partridge, Alpha Papa,
OL,14,Fand A Song For Jenny.
OL,16,FHe also made appearances in Doctors,
OL,17,FRovers and The Musketeers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]
